resources.string: Dalvik Explorer is an excellent app by Elliott Hughes that displays Java system properties, environment variables, and more.\n\nYou can download it from Play Store.

aLogcat is a great Android system log file reader by Jeffrey Blattman.

You can download it from Play Store.

Please consider his donate version if you find it useful.

ManifestViewer is a great way to get information about installed apps\' AndroidManifest.xml, including intent filters and permissions.\n\nThe app is created by susatthi and you can download it from Play Store.
